      "props": {
        "text": "YES if at least one paper (peer-reviewed journal, conference proceedings, or indexed pre-print on arXiv/SSRN/bioRxiv) cites MiroShark by name or URL in its methodology, references, or supplementary materials by September 30, 2026. Verified via Google Scholar, Semantic Scholar, or direct link to the published/pre-print paper.",
